      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 straight-six with factory individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS timing. It delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, its mechanical integrity\u2014including the variable M differential lock and high-performance braking system\u2014remains sharp for spirited B-road driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
